Title: The Great And Venerable Teacher
---
Master Yu and Master Sang were friends. Once it rained incessantly for
ten days. Master Yu said to himself, Master Sang is probably having a
bad time, and he wrapped up some rice and took it for his friend to
eat. When he got to Master Sang's gate, he heard something like singing
or crying, and someone striking a lute and sayingï¼š
